## 📅 DAY 1 — Project Skeleton + Backend

### 1.1 Create Project Folders
- [ ] Create root folder `my-edtech-app/`
- [ ] Create subfolder `my-edtech-app/backend/`
- [ ] Create subfolder `my-edtech-app/frontend/` (will be auto-created by Vite)

### 1.2 Frontend — Initialize Vite + React
- [ ] Run `npm create vite@latest frontend -- --template react`
- [ ] `cd frontend`
- [ ] Run `npm install`
- [ ] Delete the default `App.css` file (we will use Tailwind instead)
- [ ] Delete the default `src/assets/react.svg` (replace with your own logo later)
- [ ] Clear out the default code inside `App.jsx` (remove the counter example)
- [ ] Clear out the default code inside `index.css` (remove Vite default styles)

### 1.3 Frontend — Install Tailwind CSS
- [ ] Run `npm install -D tailwindcss@3 postcss autoprefixer`
- [ ] Run `npx tailwindcss init -p` (this creates `tailwind.config.js` and `postcss.config.js`)
- [ ] Open `tailwind.config.js` → set `content` to `["./index.html", "./src/**/*.{js,jsx}"]`
- [ ] Open `src/index.css` → add these 3 lines at the top:
  ```
  @tailwind base;
  @tailwind components;
  @tailwind utilities;
  ```
- [ ] Test Tailwind works: add `<h1 className="text-3xl text-red-500">Hello</h1>` in App.jsx
- [ ] Run `npm run dev` → confirm red "Hello" text shows at `localhost:5173`

### 1.4 Frontend — Install ALL Dependencies (One Command)
- [ ] Run this single command:
  ```
  npm install react-router-dom axios framer-motion recharts lucide-react @heroicons/react react-icons react-toastify react-big-calendar date-fns @hello-pangea/dnd react-hotkeys-hook react-speech-recognition regenerator-runtime pdfjs-dist react-pdf react-player react-syntax-highlighter chart.js --legacy-peer-deps
  ```
- [ ] Confirm no fatal errors (warnings are OK)

